<ref name="Windows95OS">[[Windows 95]] and later</ref>
<ref name="WindowsMobileOS">[[Windows Mobile]]</ref>
<ref name="image-dired">Activating [https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_node/emacs/Image_002dDired.html Image-Dired] command in the graphical interface.</ref>
<ref name="windowsencryption">The encryption feature in Windows 2000 Professional, Windows XP Professional, and Windows Server 2003 is in fact a user-transparent filesystem-level encryption feature for NTFS. The file manager merely enables or disables it.</ref>
